		"name": "Order Service - API",
		"description": "Colección de endpoints del servicio de ordenes y checkout sincrono.\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:8081\n\n**Alcance:**\n- Carrito\n- Órdenes\n- Checkout sincrono\n- Integración con auth-service y catalog-service\n\n**Almacenamiento:** En memoria (ConcurrentHashMap)\n**Framework:** Spring Boot 4.0.3\n**Java:** 17",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "👤 Usuarios",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Registrar Usuario",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"juan\",\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"1234\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Juan Pérez\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/register",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "users", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Registra un nuevo usuario en el sistema.\n\nValidaciones:\n- Username único\n- Email único"
					},
					"response": []
				},
